title: Help Us Support Special Olympics at Red Robin on October 22! (City of La Habra, ...
text: ( Source : City of La Habra, CA ) Help the La Habra Police Department support Special Olympics at Red Robin and meet our local athletes! When: Thursday, October 22 , from 5:00 p.m.- 9:00 p.m. Where: Red Robin-1631 W, Imperial Hwy, La Habra, CA
